   <abstract>Photograph taken by Chaliapin of following his performance in "Barber of Seville" in Russia. Gottfried Galston and his wife Sandra as well as Ferruccio Busoni and his wife Gerda are present. Gerda holds a dog in her lap and wine bottles are on the table.</abstract>
